# Restaurant Menu UI Design

## Overview

This project was created as part of the CodSoft UI/UX Internship Program. The objective was to design a visually appealing and user-friendly restaurant menu interface that helps customers browse menu categories, explore food items, and make selections with ease.

## Features

* Modern and attractive user interface
* Clear food categorization
* Easy navigation
* Clean typography
* Consistent color palette
* User-friendly layout
* Well-organized menu sections
* Enhanced visual appeal for better user engagement

